  <brief_title>Algorithms in a Simulated Difficult Intubation Scenario</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison of the Difficult Airway Society (UK) and Australian Patient Safety Foundation Crisis Algorithms for Difficult Intubation in a Simulated Difficult Intubation Scenario</official_title>
  <sponsors>
